  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the present study is to determine if the retinal thickness estimates of the
      Stratus OCT, the 3D OCT-1000, and the CirrusHD OCT are comparable in diabetic and in healthy
      individuals (OCT=Optical Coherence Tomography).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
